    <h1>The Image FieldType</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"aui-message hint shadowed information-macro">=20
<span class=3D"aui-icon icon-hint">Icon</span>=20
<div class=3D"message-content">=20
<p>FieldType identifier: <code>ezimage</code><br />Validators: File size<br=
 />Value object: <code>\eZ\Publish\Core\FieldType\Image\Value</code><span><=
br />Associated services: <code><span>ezpublish.fieldType.ezimage.variation=
_service</span></code></span></p>=20
</div>=20
</div>=20
<p><style type=3D"text/css">/*<![CDATA[*/
div.rbtoc1413886066301 {padding: 0px;}
